def: A pin worn on the breast for a fastening, or for ornament; abrooch.
The gentlemen, or gentry, of a country, collectively. [Writtenalso squirearchy.]
The radical UO2, conveniently regarded as a residue of manyuranium compounds.
Destitute of feet; as, feetless birds.
The keeper and driver of an elephant. [East Indies]
Of or pertaining to hydrometeorology, or to rain, clouds,storms, etc.
Full of augury; foreboding. [Obs.] "Augurous hearts." Chapman.
Pertaining to the west wind; soft; mild; gentle.
